Cross-Engine Dependencies
IDN integrates with but does not own:
GGP — authorization and governance
DAT — execution permissions
MUX — external credential use
FLO — financial attribution

Completion Criteria
IDN documentation is complete when:
NS-IDN-000 → NS-IDN-014 exist
Identity resolution is deterministic and auditable
Trust assertions are explicit and versioned
All engines reference identity consistently

Next engine to generate:➡️ CDE — Content Distribution Engine